@wp.kernel
def expr_cpzdwd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = float(0.0)
    v2 = float(1.0)
    tmp = float(0.0)
    v2 = v2
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v0 + 0.56 / v0 + 0.07)))
    tmp = (0.01 * v1)
    v0 = (v1 + 0.56)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.89) * wp.cos(v2 + 0.44)) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.45) * v2))
    v0 = wp.abs(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
